{"tid":102768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂] 為左上/下一代嘅母語 唔好再比佢去睇TVB","createTime":"2017-01-31T23:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T18:30:25.000Z","uid":47352,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a70dabc291f779f8180249c8b0a28e714313e0","tid":102768,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:09:36.000Z","msg":"根本TVB啲劇/新聞/甚至所有節目n年前開始全部都由識聽廣東話嘅大陸人寫字幕 <br />\n<br />\n例如近年報新聞就將希特拉叫希特勒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下呢幾句，只係用普通話讀出嚟就會好順口。<br />\n例如：吃水果 喝補藥 就要 吃吃水果 喝喝補藥<br />\n攪亂 就變咗 搞砸 <br />\n<br />\n再加埋而家小朋友個個學普教中 遲啲就算佢都係講廣東話 你都會覺得係書面語左嘅廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/065303_780664a66c74319ead64e6d6f2bb91ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F065303_780664a66c74319ead64e6d6f2bb91ae.jpg&h=c0e23ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7583CAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7583CAZ.jpg&h=5adc2d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2p4e9nB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2p4e9nB.jpg&h=f8a14910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b12b8fa5324b6c6ac57694e7659195c30e724ed5","tid":102768,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f97c48d75775db7da574a066aab3cc3f475758","tid":102768,"uid":5662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"書面語=蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6053c2b2f657a2f0801542c28404fc846b492262","tid":102768,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma